            </div>
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold" style="color:#38bdf8;flex-shrink:0;">60 %</span>
          </div>
          <div class="quiz-level quiz-level--locked">
            <div style="flex:1;">
              <div class="text-xs font-bold mb-1.5" style="color:#6e6e76;">SCHWER</div>
              <div class="quiz-bar"><div class="quiz-bar__fill" style="width:0%;"></div></div>
            </div>
            <span class="text-xs" style="color:#6e6e76;flex-shrink:0;">🔒 Gesperrt</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs mt-4" style="color:#6e6e76;">Jede Stufe schaltet nach Bestehen frei &mdash; je Enabler-Quiz 1 Versuch.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 3: Vertrauensregeln -->
        <div class="hai2-card">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
            <div class="hai2-card-icon" style="background:rgba(14,165,233,.12);">
              <svg width="18" height="18" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="#0ea5e9" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-base" style="color:#f0f0f2;">Was HAI garantiert</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="trust-row">
            <div class="trust-dot" style="background:rgba(52,211,153,.12);color:#34d399;">✓</div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-sm font-semibold mb-0.5" style="color:#e2e8f0;">Nur Kursinhalte</div>
              <div class="text-xs" style="color:#6e6e76;">Antworten kommen aus eingebetteten Materialien</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="trust-row">
            <div class="trust-dot" style="background:rgba(52,211,153,.12);color:#34d399;">✓</div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-sm font-semibold mb-0.5" style="color:#e2e8f0;">Keine erfundenen Daten</div>
              <div class="text-xs" style="color:#6e6e76;">Noten, Termine &mdash; HAI erfindet niemals Plattformdaten</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="trust-row">
            <div class="trust-dot" style="background:rgba(248,113,113,.1);color:#f87171;">✗</div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-sm font-semibold mb-0.5" style="color:#e2e8f0;">Keine fertigen Lösungen</div>
              <div class="text-xs" style="color:#6e6e76;">Bei Szenarien und Quizzen immer Leitfragen, nie Copy-Paste</div>
